name: The Spark of Creativity
description:
I chose this work to begin with, because for me it represents the spark of origin, the first one that will light the flame to be able to create much more and continue to grow in this world.
This image has been created through a long exposure, using a flame as the only lighting point and moving the camera to create particular figures.
